result.execSummary:
The defendant Jarrod L. Breivogel was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jarrod L. Breivogel is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Jarrod L. Breivogel was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
  • Jarrod L. Breivogel was found guilty of Criminal Damage to Property, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 943.01(1).
